parameters: \fi\c[17]"Fight the good fight of the faith. Take hold of
the eternal life to which you were called when you
made your good confession in the presence
\fi\c[17]"Through You, we will push back our
adversaries, through Your Name, we will trample
down those who rise up against us." Psalm 44:5
\fi\c[17]"This is what the Lord says to you: Do not
be afraid or discouraged because of this vast army,
For the battle is not yours, but God's."
